        <div class="About__flex__section text">
          <h2>Question Cubes</h2>
          <p class="first">Qubes is a group stacking game with questions, the culmination of a project designed to build communication and strengthen relationships between incarcerated fathers and their children.</p>
          <p>In a time of rising prison population, deteriorating conditions and health, and the host of problems which feed into loops of deprivation and crime.</p>
          <p>Extending the category of Social Games, Qubes was inspired by Captivated, a project South Denmark University’s Social Games Against Crime team which sought to tackle the same issue of parental alienation in prison.</p>
          <p><a href="/dev/placeholder">Read more about why Captivated worked here.</a></p>
        </div>
