        <p>Qubes uses this model in relation to building and strengthening relationships. Its questions (by colour coded blocks) are ordered on where they fall on this superficial-deep scale, superficial questions receive few points while deeper questions have more.</p>
        <p>This balance of physical tension, points motivating players to tackle more difficult subjects, allows the gameplay to prompt users to move between them as necessary.</p>
